      • setProperties

        public boolean setProperties(java.lang.String configuration)
        This function specifies the properties of the metric
        Parameters:
        configuration - properties of the metric in string format
        Returns:
        true if the string representation has a valid format, or false otherwise. String representation of properties has to have the following format:

        ATTRIBUTE-1:VALUE-1 | ATTRIBUTE-2:VALUE-2 ..... | ATTRIBUTE-K:VALUE-K

        NOTE: If the attribute names (values) are invalid, the default settings are used.
